var PCHMINIBOOTSTRAP = PCHMINIBOOTSTRAP || {};
if (typeof PCHMINIBOOTSTRAP.contentBaseURL === "undefined") PCHMINIBOOTSTRAP.contentBaseURL = "";


var invisibleDivMarkup = "<div id='invisibleDiv'></div>";
var selectedItem = "";
function initTutorial(){
		// initialize scrollable together with the navigator plugin
		$("#navigator").scrollable({
			keyboard:false,
			circular:true,
			onSeek : function(){postScroll()}
		}).navigator();
		$("#tutorial_holder").overlay({
			top:170,
			left:230,
			fixed:false,
			mask: {
		color: '#000',
		loadSpeed: 20,
		opacity: 0.7
	    },
	    closeOnClick: true,
	    load: false,
	    onClose: function(){tutorialClosed();toggleOtherLightbox(true);toggleBannerImage(true);},
	    onBeforeLoad: function(){toggleOtherLightbox(false);toggleBannerImage(false);}
	    });
		$("#tutorial_holder a").click(
				function(e){
					e.preventDefault();
					}
				);
}

function postScroll(){
			tutorialClosed();
			var tabId = $($("#navigator .items div.maindiv")[$(".scrollable").data("scrollable").getIndex()+1]).attr("id");
			var Tutsettings = 
			{
				featuredarea:{
					shownDiv:$("html").hasClass("ie")?$("#sliderholder"):$("#mainholder"),
					arrowClass:"featuredarr",
					callback:function(){
						if(!$("html").hasClass("ie")){
					$("#invisibleDiv").addClass("featuredareainvisiblediv")}else{$("#invisibleDiv").removeClass()}},
					invisibleDiv:$("html").hasClass("ie")?$("#sliderholder"):$("#mainholder")
				},
				checklist:{
					shownDiv:$(".uni-nav-bar .content"),
					arrowClass:"checklistarr",
					callback:function(){
						$("#token_center").addClass("openedFromTutorial");
						$("#token_center").hasClass("openedFromTutorial")?PCH.uniExp.tokenCenter.toggleContainer(600):0;
					},
					invisibleDiv:$(".uni-nav-bar .content,#token_center .token_center,#token_center .footer,.message-center")
				},
				navigation:{
					shownDiv:$(".nav-bar"),
					arrowClass:"navigationarr",
					callback:"",
					invisibleDiv:$(".nav-bar")
				}
			}
			selectedItem = Tutsettings[tabId];			
			if(selectedItem.shownDiv != "" && selectedItem.arrowClass != ""){
			selectedItem.shownDiv.addClass("higherz");
			$(".tutorialarrow").addClass(selectedItem.arrowClass);
			selectedItem.invisibleDiv.prepend($(invisibleDivMarkup));
			if(typeof selectedItem.callback == 'function')selectedItem.callback();
			}
}



function tutorialClosed(){
	if($("#token_center").hasClass("openedFromTutorial")){
		PCH.uniExp.tokenCenter.toggleContainer(600);
		$("#token_center").removeClass("openedFromTutorial");
	}
	$(".higherz").removeClass("higherz");
	$(".tutorialarrow").removeClass().addClass("tutorialarrow");
	$("html #invisibleDiv").remove();
}

function toggleOtherLightbox(showHide){
	//$("#tutorial_holder").overlay().getConf().left = ($(".accordion").offset().left-651.5)
	//$("#tutorial_holder").overlay().getConf().top = (136 + $(".rewards-block").offset().top)
	var lb = $(".sso-lightbox.hide");
	if(lb.length < 1){return false;}
	if(showHide){
		setTimeout(function(){lb.show()},1000);
	}
	else{
		lb.hide();
	}
}

function toggleBannerImage(showHide){
	var topBannerExists = $("#topBannerSection img").attr("src") != "/";
	if(showHide){
		topBannerExists?$("#topBannerSection").slideDown():0;
	}
	else{
		topBannerExists?$("#topBannerSection").slideUp():0;
	}
}

$( function( e ) {
	initTutorial();
	if(!PCH.tutorialShown){
		$("#tutorial_holder").overlay().load();
		$(".scrollable").data("scrollable").seekTo(0);
		$.ajax({
			url:PCHMINIBOOTSTRAP.contentBaseURL+"index.php?option=com_pchcom_content&task=setTutorialShown&format=raw"
		});
		PCH.tutorialShown = 1;
	}
});